    after some time has gone by:</p>
  <p align="left">&nbsp;</p>
  <div align="center">
    <center>
      <table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="30%">
        <tr>
          <td width="100%" background="/images/graphbackgr.gif" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"><p align="center"><br>
              <img border="0" src="{{ asset('storage/images/graph_power.gif') }}" width="282" height="166"><br>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td width="100%" bgcolor="#DFFFDF"><p align="center">Affluence leveling off at a higher level:<br>
              Power trend.</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </center>
